---
import { SITE_CONFIG } from "@/data/site"
---

<article
  class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row"
>
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
  >
    <p>
      I'm a Full-Stack Software Engineer who builds
      <strong>enterprise-scale applications, data systems, and automation
      solutions</strong>. My work spans from designing robust backend services with Java
      and Spring Boot to delivering intuitive Angular frontends backed by SQL
      Server and MySQL.
    </p>

    <p>
      On the data side, I design end-to-end BI pipelines with
      <strong>SSIS, SSAS, and Power BI</strong>, transforming raw business data into
      actionable insights. I also bring deep experience in
      <strong>web scraping, test automation with Selenium and PyTest</strong>, and
      building REST APIs with Python frameworks like FastAPI and Django.
    </p>

    <p>
      What drives me is the product-building mindset —
      <strong>taking ideas from concept to deployed solution</strong>. I'm
      particularly excited about AI-assisted modernization, using LLMs and
      code analysis to accelerate legacy migrations and unlock new capabilities
      in existing systems. You can see this across my projects — from the AI
      Migration Factory to BI solutions and enterprise ERP systems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <img
    width="200"
    height="200"
    src={SITE_CONFIG.aboutImage}
    alt="Portrait of Ali Hamdaoui"
    class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-full p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 ring-1 ring-black/70 dark:ring-white/20"
    style="object-position: 50% 50%"
  />
</article>
